HostMada is proud to announce the launch of the new OpenVZ SSD line in **Hong Kong** for all VPS services.

We have been focusing on HDD plans during these years for all our locations though after the huge demands we have finally decided to launch SSD plans as well.&lt;br&gt;
Hong Kong is the first one, an european location will come out in few weeks.

The network includes premium low latency access to **China Telecom** and **China Unicom** backbone, the HKIX for local traffic and NTT GIN for Asia and international routes. By providing direct access connectivity our chinese customers get the fastest route to mainland China as well as to the huge Chinese market itself.

To celebrate our newest location, we have a _15% recurring discount_ available on all SSD VPS at our Hong Kong data center for all new services, new clients and current clients! Just enter promotional code **HK15OFF** to receive _15% off_ every month.
 
